            "instructions": [
                "In a saucepan, heat the oil over medium heat and melt the chopped onion.",
                "Add the crushed garlic and cook for a few minutes until tender.",
                "Add the sausage slices and cook until they are well browned.",
                "Add the peeled and diced tomato and the tomato paste. Mix well.",
                "Season with salt and pepper and add thyme and bay leaves if desired.",
